# =============================================================================
# Susi Air Pilot App — environment variables
#
# Copy to `.env` for local dev. NEVER commit real API keys. The runtimeConfig
# in nuxt.config.ts maps these to server-only `runtimeConfig.gemini*` values
# (they are NEVER exposed to the client bundle — do not move to .public).
# =============================================================================

# Gemini API keys — comma-separated. Round-robins on each request, retrying
# the next key only on HTTP 429 (rate limit).
# NUXT_GEMINI_API_KEYS=key_one,key_two

# Single-key fallback used when the comma list above is unset.
# NUXT_GEMINI_API_KEY=your_key_here
